The revised liquidation budget for MONUA for the 1999/00 financial period represents an increase of 51 per cent in gross terms ($7,607,900), compared with the original budget for the same period, and reflects the absorption of the commitment authority of $5,274,800 gross ($4,875,100 net) granted by the Advisory Committee (see para.
