I. Introduction
At its 90th plenary meeting, on 2 March 2000, the General Assembly, on the proposal of the Secretary-General (A/54/237), decided to include in the agenda of its fifty-fourth session the item entitled “Financing of the United Nations Organization Mission in the Democratic Republic of the Congo” and to allocate it to the Fifth Committee.
