The Acting President: In view of the urgency unanimously expressed by Member States that a decision on the organizational aspects of the Millennium Summit should be taken without delay, I have consulted with the Secretariat and I can advise Member States that if draft resolution A/54/L.83/Rev.1 is adopted today, it will be possible to have the drawing of lots to establish the list of speakers for the Millennium Summit on Friday, 26 May, in the morning.
